<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.6.1">
<l>mainniṉṟa karuṅkaṭalvā yulakiṉṟi vāṉavarum yāmumellām</l>
<l>neynniṉṟa cakkarattaṉ tiruvayiṟṟil neṭuṅkālam kiṭantatōrīr</l>
<l>ennaṉṟi ceytārā vētilōr teyvattai yēttukiṉṟīr</l>
<l>ceynnaṉṟi kuṉṟēṉmiṉ toṇṭarkā ḷaṇṭaṉaiyē yēttīrkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You do not understand the long-time repose in the black sea</l>
<l rend="indent">where darkness persisted without the world,</l>
<l>Of the one with the discus where blood persists, [and] the celestials,</l>
<l rend="indent">all things, and us in his divine belly.</l>
<l>You are praising the deity of outsiders being those who does what good?</l>
<l>Do not neglect [proper] gratitude, devotees!</l>
<l rend="indent">Praise only the one who is the universe!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
